reviewText: explanations are not clear and all can be found on youtube for free

First i am a twisted sister fan so i'm biased. second he plays alot of parts fast and a small few parts might be left out. but i think even a beginner could get "were not gonna take it" and "i wanna rock" pretty fast. The tab is on the disk in pdf form so you don't have to worry about downloading it on the net from a site that might not exsist. i think he's a better player than an instructor but again as a fan i'm biased. this dvd is very cool!
It's amazing for me to hear "the price" stripped down to one guitar.
